title: Israelis, Palestinians Weigh Extent of Donald Trump’s Shift - WSJ
text:
TEL AVIV—Many Israelis and Palestinians see President Donald Trump’s decision to stop pushing for a two-state solution to the conflict as a significant change of tone—but not necessarily one of substance.
